<br>
<br>
Dear Dr. Laura: <br>
<br>
Thank you for doing so much to educate people regarding God's Law. I <br>
have learned a great deal from your show, and try to share that knowledge with as many people as I can. When someone tries to defend the homosexual lifestyle, for example, I simply remind them that Leviticus 18:22 clearly states it to be an abomination. I do need some advice from you, however, regarding some of the other specific laws and how to follow them. <br>
<br>
